    "details": [
      "🏡 Number #1 Choice for Domestic Use: Specifically designed for households, societies, and residential buildings, this digital starter gives residents 100% freedom from the daily hassle of monitoring water levels and manually switching the motor off.\n\n⚡ Best Suited for Up to 2 HP Motors: This starter is incredibly powerful and perfectly optimized to handle all types of single-phase motors and domestic borehole submersible pumps ranging from 0.5 HP up to a maximum capacity of 2 HP.\n\n🥇 Trust of Brand Param Automation: Built with advanced microcontroller technology, this single-phase starter is one of India's safest, most modern, and highly reliable motor protection systems for residential pumps.\n\n🛡️ Drastic Increase in Motor Lifespan: This starter doubles the life of your valuable single-phase motor by isolating it from dangerous grid surges, high/low voltage conditions, and dry running, saving you from the heavy recurring costs of motor rewinding.\n\n💯 1-Year Full Warranty: Param Automation offers a rock-solid 1-year comprehensive warranty, standing as direct proof of our product's premium build quality, rugged durability, and stellar performance.\n\n⚙️ Fully Customizable Settings: Equipped with user-friendly setting buttons, this panel allows you to customize all parameters—such as current thresholds, voltage cut-offs, and timers—exactly according to your domestic motor's specific requirements.\n\n🔌 Integrated Start & Run Capacitor Control: The advanced internal circuitry precisely regulates the starting capacitor (to easily lift the pump load on startup) and the running capacitor (for continuous operation), ensuring your 2 HP motor starts smoothly every single time.\n\n📡 Fully Automatic Home Water Management (100m to 2km Remote Range): A true blessing for modern homes, you can wire 2-wire magnetic float sensors to completely automate your rooftop overhead tank and underground sump cycles. Additionally, it supports wireless remote kits with various models available ranging from 100 meters up to a massive 2-kilometer line-of-sight range, allowing you to control the pump from any room, balcony, or terrace.\n\n🌊 Zero Water Wastage — Lowers Electricity & Water Bills: Homes often suffer from overhead tanks overflowing, which damages roofs and inflates electricity bills. The integrated sensor system detects a full tank and shuts off the motor within milliseconds, conserving water and saving money.\n\n⏱️ Smart Dry-Run and On-Time Timer: If your household well or borehole runs out of water, the starter immediately trips the motor to prevent damage and automatically restarts it after your pre-set duration (configured in minutes) once the water source replenishes.\n\n⏳ Built-in Motor Run Timer (Valid ONLY in MANUAL Mode): Never worry about forgetting to turn off the pump again! You can set a fixed operating duration (in minutes), and the starter will automatically shut down the motor when the time is up. (Please note: This timer remains inactive when operating in Auto/Sensor Mode).\n\n🎯 Precise Digital Overload Protection: If sand enters the pump or a severe voltage drop forces the single-phase motor to draw current above your safe pre-set limit, the smart electronic sensors trip the system instantly to guard the internal windings.\n\n📉 High and Low Voltage Cut-off (Domestic Safeguard): Residential power lines frequently experience severe voltage drops or dangerous voltage surges (such as double-phasing spikes) due to heavy appliances like ACs and refrigerators. This starter immediately disconnects the motor during unsafe voltage levels and only permits a restart once the power stabilizes back to normal.\n\n🖥️ Live Digital Display Screen: The high-tech digital monitor displays your home's real-time single-phase line voltage (V) along with the active motor load current (Amperes), removing the need to ever purchase or install a separate voltmeter.\n\n🛠️ Long Life and Zero Maintenance: Unlike traditional thermal starters, this solid-state system has no moving mechanical parts, completely eliminating common issues like carbon deposits or burnt contactors for an entirely maintenance-free experience.\n\n🔌 Built-in Auto Switch: This panel features an integrated automatic switch, meaning you don't have to manually restart the panel after a power cut. It safely samples the incoming grid voltage as soon as electricity returns and safely restarts the motor on its own.\n\n⛈️ Moisture Protection & Crucial Warranty Clause: This digital starter houses delicate microcontroller components and must be protected from water spray and damp conditions at all costs. If installed in outdoor areas prone to rain or splashing, always cover it with a waterproof shield or housing. Please note that any device failure caused by water ingress, humidity, or internal moisture exposure will completely void the 1-year warranty."
    ],
