    "short": "🥇 Trust of Brand Param Automation: Built with advanced microcontroller technology, the Param Automation starter is one of India's safest and most modern motor protection systems.\n\n🛡️ Drastic Increase in Motor Life: This starter doubles the lifespan of your valuable motor by protecting it from fatal voltage fluctuations and dry running, saving you from the heavy recurring costs of motor rewinding.\n\n💯 1-Year Full Warranty: Param Automation offers a solid 1-year comprehensive warranty, which stands as direct proof of our product's unmatched quality, durability, and stellar performance.\n\n💪 Powerful Performance: This heavy-duty digital starter effortlessly handles all types of 3-phase motors and submersible pumps up to 7.5 HP with an adjustable load capacity of up to 22 Amperes (Amp).\n\n⚙️ Fully Customizable Settings: Equipped with easy-to-use setting buttons, this starter allows you to customize all parameters—such as current limits, voltage limits, and timers—exactly according to your motor's specific requirements.\n\n📡 Remote and Sensor Enabled (Up to 2 KM Range): This advanced device comes automation-ready, allowing you to connect water level sensors for automated overhead and underground tank management, or plug in our heavy-duty wireless remote-control kit for flawless, long-distance operation up to a massive 2-kilometre range.\n\n⏱️ Smart Dry-Run and On-Time Timer: When the water source runs dry, the starter immediately stops the motor to prevent damage and automatically restarts it after your pre-set delay time (e.g., 1 or 2 hours) once water replenishes.\n\n⏳ Built-in Motor Run Timer: No more worrying about forgetting to turn off the motor! You can set a fixed operating duration (e.g., 1 or 2 hours), and the starter will automatically shut down the motor when the time is up, saving water and electricity.\n\n🔄 Anti-Reverse Rotation Protection: If the phase sequence alters from the main supply line, this intelligent starter prevents the motor from running in reverse, completely eliminating the risk of physical damage to your submersible pump.\n\n⚡ Full Single-Phasing Prevention: If any one of the incoming three phases drops or gets weak, the starter cuts power within milliseconds, ensuring the motor never burns out by running on two phases.\n\n🎯 Precise Digital Overload Protection: If the motor jams due to sand or bearing issues and draws current above your set limit (up to 22 Amp), the smart electronic sensors trip the system instantly to guard the windings.\n\n📉 High and Low Voltage Cut-off: During extreme voltage drops or surges, Param Automation isolates the motor from the grid and only permits a restart once the voltage stabilizes back to a completely safe operating zone.\n\n🖥️ Live Digital Display Screen: The high-tech digital monitor displays the real-time voltage of all three phases along with the active load current (Amperes), removing the need to ever open the starter box for manual testing.\n\n🛠️ Long Life and Zero Maintenance: Unlike traditional thermal starters, this solid-state system has no moving mechanical parts, eliminating issues like carbon deposits or burnt contactors for an entirely maintenance-free experience.\n\n🔌 Built-in Auto Switch: This panel features an integrated automatic switch, completely removing the need to purchase or wire an external auto-switch device. It safely restarts the motor on its own as soon as power returns.",
